@post_election
on-arrival: {!
// set congress proportion to votes
Q.spd_r = Q.spd_votes;
Q.z_r = Q.z_votes;
Q.kpp_r = Q.kpp_votes;
Q.psl-w_r = Q.psl-w_votes;
Q.npr_r = Q.npr_votes;
Q.sn_r = Q.sn_votes;
Q.owp_r = Q.owp_votes;
Q.other_r = Q.other_votes;

// The largest party can only be the OWP or the SPD.
Q.largest_party = 'SPD';
if (Q.owp_r >= Q.spd_r && Q.owp_r >= Q.kpp_r) {
    Q.largest_party = 'OWP';
}
if (Q.kpp_r >= Q.spd_r && Q.kpp_r >= Q.owp_r) {
    Q.largest_party = 'KPP';
}

// coalitions
Q.weimar_coalition = Q.spd_r + Q.psl-w_r + Q.z_r - 3;
Q.grand_coalition = Q.spd_r + Q.psl-w_r + Q.z_r + Q.npr_r;
Q.bourgeois_coalition = Q.psl-w_r + Q.z_r + Q.npr_r + Q.other_r;
Q.center_right_coalition = Q.z_r + Q.psl-w_r + Q.npr_r + Q.other_r + Q.sn_r;
Q.right_coalition = Q.z_r + Q.npr_r + Q.other_r + Q.sn_r;
Q.far_right_coalition = Q.sn_r + Q.owp_r;
Q.left_coalition = Q.spd_r + Q.kpp_r;
// this is an absurd concept lol
Q.united_front_coalition = Q.spd_r + Q.kpp_r + Q.z_r + Q.psl-w_r - 3;
Q.anti_democratic_coalition = Q.kpp_r + Q.owp_r;
// aka everyone except nazi, kpp, sn
Q.neo_weimar_coalition = Q.spd_r + Q.psl-w_r + Q.z_r + Q.npr_r + Q.other_r;
!}

The electoral system is essentially proportional, with the proportion of Reichstag seats roughly equal to the proportion of votes.
 
**Election results:**

# 1928: 30, 1930: 25, 1932: 22
SPD: [+ spd_r +]

# 1928: 15, 1930: 15, 1932: 
Z + BVP: [+ z_r +]

# 1928: 10, 1930: 13
KPP: [+ kpp_r +]

# 1928: 5, 1930: 4 (as DstP)
PSL-W: [+ psl-w_r +]

# 1928: 9, 1930: 5
NPR: [+ npr_r +]

# 1928: 14, 1930: 7
SN: [+ sn_r +]

# 1928: 3, 1930: 18
OWP: [+ owp_r +]

# 1928: 9, 1930: 10
Other: [+ other_r +]

**Potential coalitions:**

Weimar Coalition (SPD + Z + PSL-W): [+ weimar_coalition +]

Grand Coalition (SPD + Z + BVP + PSL-W + NPR): [+ grand_coalition +]

Bourgeois Coalition (Z + BVP + PSL-W + NPR + Others): [+ bourgeois_coalition +]

Right-wing Coalition (Z + BVP + NPR + Others + SN): [+ right_coalition +]

